---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us | Nordam Enterprises">
  <!-- Use a main container with vertical padding -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">

    <!-- ===== SECTION 1: ABOUT US + TEAM PHOTO ===== -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Text -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">ABOUT US</h1>
        <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
          <p>Since 1993, Nordam Enterprises has been a trusted, family-owned business at the heart of Malawiâ€™s power sector. We specialize in providing robust and reliable power solutions, from high-performance diesel generators and industrial engines to advanced solar power systems and energy storage. Our team of highly-qualified engineers, electricians, and mechanics brings decades of combined experience, ensuring expert service and support for every project.</p>
          <p>Our commitment extends beyond just supplying quality products from leading brands like Perkins, Lister Petter, and FG Wilson. We offer a comprehensive suite of services including professional installation, ongoing maintenance, and 24/7 support to keep your operations running smoothly. We strive to build long-term relationships with our customers by providing exceptional, personalized service tailored to your unique needs.</p>
          <p>We are proud to be the power solutions partner for a wide range of clients in Lilongwe and across Malawi, including the United States Embassy, German Embassy, British High Commission, European Union, and numerous banks, NGOs, schools, and hospitals. Our goal is to continue leading the power sector by delivering quality and reliability where it matters most.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Image -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <img src="/images/team-photo.jpg" alt="The Nordam Enterprises Team" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-xl" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== SECTION 2: MAP + FIND US ===== -->
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16 mt-24 md:mt-32">

      <!-- Left Column: Map -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d4560.520095598337!2d33.781550691092505!3d-13.910957300097058!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1921d4dab4f0d075%3A0x13eb5fa6222459de!2sNordam%20Enterprises!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smw!4v1752163603276!5m2!1sen!2smw" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>

      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Text -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">FIND US</h2>
        <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Area 28, Plot 130, Lilongwe<br/>
            P.O. Box 879
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ===== SECTION 3: FOLLOW US ===== -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16 mt-24 md:mt-32">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Text -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
  ^   <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">FOLLOW US</h2>
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p class="mb-6">Stay up to date with our latest news, projects, and offers by following us on social media.</p>
        <a href="https://web.facebook.com/NordamEnt" class="btn btn-outline text-primary border-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white">Find us on Facebook</a>
      </div>
    </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Illustration -->
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <img src="/images/social-illustration.png" alt="Illustration of social media" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-xl" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  </div>
</Layout>




